## TaskMaster - Task Management Application

**Creator & Developer:** Krish Yadav  
**Project Type:** Open Source Web Application  
**License:** MIT License  

### About This Project

TaskMaster is a modern, feature-rich task management application designed to help users organize their daily tasks efficiently. Built with cutting-edge web technologies including React, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, and Shadcn UI components.

### Key Features

- ✅ Comprehensive task management with priority levels and deadlines
- 🎨 Modern, responsive design with dark/light mode support
- 📊 Analytics and achievement system
- 📅 Interactive calendar with advanced date selection
- 🔄 Drag and drop task reordering
- 🎯 Priority-based task organization
- 🏆 Achievement and progress tracking system
- 🔔 Notification system for task updates
- 👤 User profiles with customizable preferences
- 🎭 Theme customization (Light/Dark/System)

